cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper focuses on road detection through sensory input and machine learning models, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The use of machine learning models also suggests a potential fit for the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing for the annotation of the dataset, which could potentially fit under the computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
